        correct: 2,
        rationale: "Beta-blockers (metoprolol) are the preferred rate control agents in HFrEF. Non-dihydropyridine CCBs (diltiazem, verapamil) are CONTRAINDICATED in HFrEF due to their negative inotropic effect which can worsen heart failure. Flecainide is contraindicated in structural heart disease due to proarrhythmic risk."
